column2: "Oh my. Oh my my! Lisa could have sworn she detected a Darker."
"Have you seen it?! It was right over here! It was such a strong Darker signal too!"

"Unless... Oh! Unless!! What if YOU are the Darker Lisa picked up?!
Hehe. Hehehe."
"Joking. That was a joke. Oh, don't give Lisa that look. Lisa can joke around too, you know?"
"But but but! If you made any sudden movements before Lisa said she was joking, it would have stopped being a joke, you know?!"
"Do you understand? What Lisa's trying to say is... Don't work yourself so hard, you know?"
"Although, that doesn't mean you have to stop doing what you have to do, you know? Just do what you want to do."
"Whatever it is you have to do, Lisa will still be shooting and shooting and KILLING and KILLING and KILLING Darkers."
"See? Just do what you want to do. That's what Lisa's doing, you know? Hehe. Hehehe."
